        <ontology:isPresentedBefore rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/narrative/N91_VC_05_SCA/event/ev11"/>
        <ontology:is_identified_by rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/appellation/Innovation"/>
        <ontology:partOfNarrative rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/narrative/N91_VC_05_SCA"/>
        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/phenomenal_place/61.21800238534556_8.474623879406925"/>
        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/place/0"/>
        <ontology:hasDescription>The type of innovation of this VC (Value Chain) is Exogenous. The innovation is about adding value to the VC with touristic packages. In addition, many of the farmers are now involved in regional projects of rural development, thus gaining attention and support through the website of those projects. In addition, e-commerce is an increasing business also for this traditional VC. The innovation is related to New products and New marketing strategies. The land use systems involved are Grassland and Natural land. The local assets include Natural, social and cultural.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


