        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/place/0"/>
        <ontology:hasDescription>1) Competing meat industry, and access to markets; 2) The need to add value to this VC because of its lower production capacity; 3) Climate change will also affect these ecosystems with increasing temperatures and precipitations as well as shorter winter seasons. Overall the type of challenge faced by this VC is Current and Predicted. This VC is classified as Traditional and Innovative.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


